    "body": "@niksingh710 I don't remember how I made it work exactly, right now I switched to a method where I use an alias for the new `nix shell` command so that the `IN_NIX_SHELL` variable is present, which is how the classic `nix-shell` was detected.\r\nAlso, due to [how](https://github.com/starship/starship/blob/cf361444d92703f0240a79b168837d8e8e844e97/src/modules/nix_shell.rs#L32-L41) the heuristics works, if you have anything with a nix store path in your PATH, it would trip the heuristic detection, which is why I switched : false positives.\r\n\r\n[Here](https://github.com/leana8959/.files/blob/5fe9ac007cbf949f079ec36bdd7fb5f314da49da/nix/homeModules/fish/functions/%2C.fish#L12)'s the alias. The function is inspired by comma\r\n\r\n\r\nHope this helps",
